{"tid":1964443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【嚴重違規】百度App多個頻道今起暫停更新 負責人遭網信辦約談","createTime":"2020-04-08T22:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T01:08:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04bc0f55b4310b61b26a35b73d06eca79c8afb6d","tid":1964443,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:04:16.000Z","msg":"國家互聯網信息辦公室發佈公告指，昨日，網信辦指導北京市網信辦，針對百度App多個頻道存在嚴重違規問題，嚴肅約談百度公司負責人，要求立即停止違規行為。百度App推薦頻道、圖片頻道、視頻頻道、財經頻道、科技頻道自今早9時起暫停更新，清理違規內容，並展開深入整改。<br />\n<br />\n北京市聯信辦有關負責人指出，百度App違反國家有關互聯網法律法規和管理要求，落實主要責任不力，大量傳播低俗庸俗訊息、密集發佈「標題黨」文章、公眾賬號註冊管理及內容審核不嚴，傳播秩序和生態問題突出，社會影響惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n4月8日上午消息，根據有關部門的整改要求，百度App部份頻道自今早9時起停止更新，進入維護狀態。百度公司負責人回應事件時表示，將嚴格落實管理要求，切實履行主要責任，對違規問題進行全面整改，暫停有關頻道更新，關閉違規賬號，嚴肅處理責任人。同時，加強內部管理，健全完善訊息安全管理機制，確保類似問題不再發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/TacARbC4NQM1xSP1D_SZRKGLMNk=/802x450/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CKEFFWRLARY3HSJ2UTMV2AT66Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FTacARbC4NQM1xSP1D_SZRKGLMNk%3D%2F802x450%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCKEFFWRLARY3HSJ2UTMV2AT66Q.jpg&h=95f29477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200408/2J2E5G6B5GX3Y7MVLUXIEL7ZOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200408%2F2J2E5G6B5GX3Y7MVLUXIEL7ZOA%2F&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=bcc562d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200408%2F2J2E5G6B5GX3Y7MVLUXIEL7ZOA%2F&h=04997671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200408/2J2E5G6B5GX3Y7MVLUXIEL7ZOA/</a>"},{"pid":"64f64044bd249c16167d742a07347dc537a71155","tid":1964443,"uid":235754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:05:25.000Z","msg":"西朝鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f329ebc7160947b5e6b530cda99ebe447d64c5fb","tid":1964443,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b731be29ff37813cfdc863fcbdeec9ac90f460","tid":1964443,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:24:25.000Z","msg":"咁百度又真係一向仆街"},{"pid":"d58c7005fc1f5bd2582ba2a3027d750a72eb6174","tid":1964443,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89b731be29ff37813cfdc863fcbdeec9ac90f460","tid":1964443,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:24:25.000Z","msg":"咁百度又真係一向仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T01:08:03.000Z","msg":"所以終於都要收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}